			</classificationInformation>
			<CASNumber>7727-54-0</CASNumber>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">An ionic compound consisting of two ammonium ions and a persulfate ion. It appears as a white, odorless single crystal with strong oxidation and corrosion properties. It decomposes easily when heated, is not prone to moisture absorption, and is soluble in water, with increased solubility in warm water. In aqueous solution, it can hydrolyze into ammonium hydrogen sulfate and hydrogen peroxide. It is used as an oxidizing agent in various industries and as a component in batter for commercially processed foods.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">由两个铵离子和一个过硫酸根离子组成的离子化合物。它呈白色无味单晶体，具有很强的氧化和腐蚀性。加热时容易分解，不易吸潮，易溶于水，在温水中的溶解度增加。在水溶液中，它能水解成硫酸氢铵和过氧化氢。它在各种工业中用作氧化剂，也是商业加工食品面糊的一种成分。</common:generalComment>
			<sumFormula>(NH4)2S2O8</sumFormula>
